}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The FCC listing mentions both a Router and Satellite device but only lists the RBS50Y model. FCC Test Report documents describe the difference between this updated RBS50Y and [Netgear Orbi Outdoor Satellite (RBS50Y)|the original] as follows... : "The differences compared with the original report (BV ADT report no.: RF170905C13-1 and RF170905C13A-1) is removing BT LE function to apply a new FCC ID: PY318400432."
*Web GUI: http://orbilogin.com
